{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 19,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always was very important to me, you know, when they were killing such-- in such a way, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is now part of our-- of our history, of our taking care of ourselves.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, it was just, how can you do such a thing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I can never approve such a thing in-- in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was aware, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, sure, aware of the Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the thing is, you know, Hitler didn't want to stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] want to do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gypsies, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can-- full of millions of people, you know, to be dead, you know, for what?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did they do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They killed themselves at the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- I can't approve such a thing for any reason, there is no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, most-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where I was at, the only thing I knew were only Jewish people coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in the crematorium, I don't think there were no other people, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there were, might be few that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But 99.9% were Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From-- that is that Hitler wanted to eliminate from life were that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I got into life very fast, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- when I went from-- when I got from the camps, and I got liberated, I was liberated with Shlomo, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Shlomo got sick on our way going to-- to Rome.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took him up to the-- the facility to-- where he couldn't breath or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He stayed there for a few years, you know, got well, and then got back to Rome, when he met [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Marica ?] and got married and they had five beautiful children.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
